# SSHD Log Security Analysis
# Detects common attack patterns and suspicious activities

note: Checking for suspicious SSH activities

# 1. Failed login attempts (brute force indicators)
note: Detecting failed login attempts
regexp: Failed \s+ password
generator: <<CODE
!python
from sparrow6lib import *

if len(matched()) > 0:
  print("assert: 1 failed password attempt detected")
  print("note: Total failed attempts: {}".format(len(matched())))
  print("note: Last 10 failed login attempts:")
  last_ten = matched()[-10:]
  for entry in last_ten:
    print("note:   {}".format(entry))
else:
  print("assert: 1 no failed attempts found")
CODE

